					<a class="blog-title-link blog-link" href="//www.mannywaks.com/blog/rabbi-yeshayahu-rizkhan-sentenced-for-child-rape">"Rabbi" Yeshayahu Rizkhan sentenced for child rape</a>

			</h2>
			<p class="blog-date">
					<span class="date-text">
		14/4/2018
	</span>

			</p>
			<p class="blog-comments">
					<a href="//www.mannywaks.com/blog/rabbi-yeshayahu-rizkhan-sentenced-for-child-rape#comments" class="blog-link">
